imdb.plot outline: Travel Wild is a positive exploration of our beautiful environment, the places and the animals that make eco-travel one of the fastest growing sectors in the leisure and travel industry. It features the best in eco-travel adventure. It takes the audience to places they have never dreamed of going, and once there, they can see how locals fight to keep their destination so special.
